*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form INIT_PROG
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& 프로그램 전역변수 초기화
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM init_prog .

  "**********************************************************************
  "* 선택조건
  "**********************************************************************
  DATA : ls_cond TYPE zrdacl_prj001=>ty_s_cond.

  ls_cond-s_prjid   = s_prjid[].
  ls_cond-s_listid  = s_listid[].
  ls_cond-s_listnm  = s_listnm[].
  ls_cond-s_keytext = s_status[].
  ls_cond-s_lityp   = s_listy[].
  ls_cond-s_mod     = s_mod[].
  ls_cond-s_cls_cd  = s_cls_cd[].
  ls_cond-s_des_id  = s_des_id[].
  ls_cond-s_dev_id  = s_dev_id[].
  ls_cond-s_tet_id  = s_tet_id[].

  IF go_0100_rep IS NOT BOUND.
    CREATE OBJECT go_0100_rep
      EXPORTING
        is_cond = ls_cond.
  ENDIF.

ENDFORM.


*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form GET_DATA
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& 데이터검색
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM get_data .

  go_0100_rep->ma_get_data( ).

ENDFORM.


*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form CALL_SCREEN
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& 화면호출
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM call_screen.

  CALL SCREEN 0100.

ENDFORM.


*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& Form FREE_DATA
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
*& 전역변수 초기화
*&---------------------------------------------------------------------*
FORM free_data .

  IF go_0100_rep IS BOUND.
    go_0100_rep->md_free_data( ).
  ENDIF.

ENDFORM.


